### Fei CHEN<img src="C:\Users\reglliu\Desktop\微信图片_20191004213528.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" />

Department of Chinese and Bilingual Studies

Research Centre for Language, Cognition, and Neuroscience

The Hong Kong Polytechnic University

E-mail: <chenfeianthony@gmail.com>



Fei Chen received the M.S. degree in linguistics from Nankai University, Tianjin, China. He is currently a Ph.D. candidate at the Department of Chinese and Bilingual Studies, Research Centre for Language, Cognition, and Neuroscience, The Hong Kong Polytechnic University. His current Ph.D. project is on 'Speech sound perception and production in tone language speaking children with autism spectrum disorders'. His current research interests include psycholinguistics, language acquisition, and pathological linguistics.

Research profile: https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Fei_Chen95 

